{"tid":1426476,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"澳洲提升對港旅遊警示","createTime":"2019-08-07T02:28:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T02:30:41.000Z","uid":1121,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"6f68f901695fe801e90d1a79cb1a46ca8dc195a5","tid":1426476,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T02:28:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://images-news.now.com/newsimage/NewsImage/AUS-TRAVEL-190807-06.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-news.now.com%2Fnewsimage%2FNewsImage%2FAUS-TRAVEL-190807-06.jpg&h=3e55d769&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/SqlRizhwH0w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FSqlRizhwH0w&d=QE5rvD4iboeChbAAuj3apP%2BqeKGcMvuhkm4gAZs5aLs%3D&h=22981dcd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/SqlRizhwH0w</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】因應本港反修例示威持續，澳洲提升對本港的旅遊警示至第二級的「高度警戒」級別。<br />\n<br />\n澳洲外交部指出，本港的「快閃」示威和針對示威者的隨機襲擊變得更難預測，並預料會持續，旅遊區和住宅區已受影響。<br />\n<br />\n澳洲外交部又指，示威人士與警方或有犯罪背景人士之間有很高的暴力衝突風險，特別是在未經授權的示威活動，晚間、周末和公眾假期的風險會更大，強烈建議正身處本港的澳洲國民，避免參與大型公眾集會，留意本港傳媒報道以及遵循港府的指示。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=358223&amp;refer=Share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D358223%26refer%3DShare&d=QE5rvD4iboeChbAAuj3apP%2BqeKGcMvuhkm4gAZs5aLs%3D&h=fee5c65b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D358223%26refer%3DShare&h=907f3cda\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=358223&amp;refer=Share</a>"},{"pid":"cb2b6780b3b0a48d095224e0042c45d34eb980a0","tid":1426476,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T02:30:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://smartraveller.gov.au/Countries/asia/north/Pages/hong_kong.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsmartraveller.gov.au%2FCountries%2Fasia%2Fnorth%2FPages%2Fhong_kong.aspx&d=QE5rvD4iboeChbAAuj3apP%2BqeKGcMvuhkm4gAZs5aLs%3D&h=d8081bd7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://smartraveller.gov.au/Countries/asia/north/Pages/hong_kong.aspx</a>"}]}